reviewText: Please correct the refund on order 104-2701569-974820. I received $122.97 instead of $12.53!!! See my e-mail of 14 January 2010.
I love Greys! My boyfriend and I watched the entire series in three months. It's addicting and very fun!

I was very happy first by the outstanding services and efficiency of amazon.com as in less than 10 days after release i received my order.
And of course by the selection of the 4 seasons of Grey's Anatomy a serie that i adore....
Looking forward the release of season 5 so i can order it from Amazon.com
Keep on the good work!!!!!
I love Grey's Anatomy. Being in Okinawa I am  missing the show so it was worth every penny!!
